      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, sensitivity analysis of model inputs is not required; nominal input values must be documented.",
      "rationale": "All model input parameters (fluid viscosity, density, hemolysis power law coefficients) are documented with sources. Formal sensitivity analysis is not required at MRL 2."
    },
