    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 requirements for Model Risk Level 2 Class II device assessment. The CFD hemolysis prediction model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions within the CPB application domain as described in the package narrative. This model has been applied in clinical research to support device design optimization. The assessment team accepts the model for the stated purpose under the Minimal profile submission.",
